syntax.responsive_grid:
.gallery
{
 display: grid;
 grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit,
minmax(250px, 1fr));
 gap: 20px;
}

syntax.flex_nav:
.nav {
 display: flex;

justify-content: space-between;
 align-items: center;
}

frequently_asked_questions.answer:
Use 'position: sticky;
top: 0;' on your header element. Ensure no parent container has 'overflow:
hidden' as it can break sticky positioning.
